734
01:00:46,659 --> 01:00:49,039
Well, then read me the book.

735
01:00:49,362 --> 01:00:51,362
[HANK SIGHS]

736
01:00:55,468 --> 01:00:57,660
You know where your name comes from?

737
01:00:57,670 --> 01:01:00,434
-My mother?
-No, before that.

738
01:01:01,140 --> 01:01:04,701
You're named after King David.
Your mother didn't tell you that?

739
01:01:04,711 --> 01:01:06,711
That figures.

740
01:01:11,351 --> 01:01:13,309
All right. Ahem.

741
01:01:13,319 --> 01:01:17,880
There were two great armies assembled,
the Israelites and the Philistines.

742
01:01:17,890 --> 01:01:20,850
They were both up on hills,
the Valley of Elah in between.

743
01:01:20,860 --> 01:01:23,219
It's in Palestine, you know where it is?

744
01:01:23,229 --> 01:01:24,587
-No.
-Doesn't matter.

745
01:01:24,597 --> 01:01:27,912
Anyway, the Philistines had a champion.

746
01:01:28,301 --> 01:01:31,065
A huge giant...

747
01:01:31,237 --> 01:01:33,029
...named Goliath.

748
01:01:33,039 --> 01:01:35,431
Really? There's a robot named Goliath.

749
01:01:35,441 --> 01:01:37,200
-This is a different guy.
-Oh.

750
01:01:37,210 --> 01:01:40,668
So every day, for 40 days...

751
01:01:40,847 --> 01:01:43,706
...Goliath would stride down
into the valley...

752
01:01:43,716 --> 01:01:47,243
...and challenge somebody from the
other side to fight, but nobody would.

753
01:01:47,253 --> 01:01:51,381
All the bravest and strongest warriors
that the king had were all too scared.

754
01:01:51,391 --> 01:01:54,917
-Why didn't they just shoot him?
-They didn't have guns.

755
01:01:54,927 --> 01:01:57,220
They had arrows,
but there are rules to combat.

756
01:01:57,230 --> 01:02:01,691
You don't shoot somebody that's
challenging you to fight with a sword.

757
01:02:01,701 --> 01:02:03,701
