804
01:05:43,586 --> 01:05:45,626
MIKE [IN VOICEOVER]:
Dad?

805
01:05:49,458 --> 01:05:51,458
Daddy?

806
01:05:55,698 --> 01:05:57,389
Something happened, Dad.

807
01:05:57,399 --> 01:05:59,399
[GASPS]

808
01:06:04,373 --> 01:06:07,069
