819
01:07:03,532 --> 01:07:05,057
Hello.

820
01:07:05,067 --> 01:07:07,192
I saw the picture of your son
in the paper.

821
01:07:07,202 --> 01:07:10,362
When you came in,
I thought he was just missing.

822
01:07:10,372 --> 01:07:12,031
I'm sorry.

823
01:07:12,041 --> 01:07:14,041
Thank you.

824
01:07:15,844 --> 01:07:17,703
May I?

825
01:07:17,713 --> 01:07:19,713
Mm.

826
01:07:24,420 --> 01:07:26,420
