saying Mike can walk.

878
01:10:43,886 --> 01:10:46,912
So Mike grabs him and they just
start going off on each other.

879
01:10:46,922 --> 01:10:50,015
But it's the kind of shit
that happens all the time.

880
01:10:50,025 --> 01:10:52,490
The whole macho-warrior crap.

881
01:10:52,561 --> 01:10:54,219
Nobody got hurt.

882
01:10:54,229 --> 01:10:56,989
So we got in the car,
we drove around for a while.

883
01:10:56,999 --> 01:11:00,225
And then we stopped at the Chicken Shack,
across from the base.

884
01:11:00,235 --> 01:11:03,128
Mike bought, for getting us kicked out.

885
01:11:03,138 --> 01:11:06,368
-And what time was this?
-I don't know.

886
01:11:07,142 --> 01:11:08,934
Around 1.

887
01:11:08,944 --> 01:11:11,378
And then we came back here.

888
01:11:14,650 --> 01:11:16,650
All of you?

889
01:11:17,486 --> 01:11:19,077
No.

890
01:11:19,087 --> 01:11:21,087
Just the three of us.

891
01:11:23,492 --> 01:11:25,450
Why would you leave him there?

892
01:11:25,460 --> 01:11:27,460
Because we were wasted.

893
01:11:27,596 --> 01:11:31,456
We had had enough,
but Mike wanted to find some meth.

894
01:11:31,466 --> 01:11:32,791
