ran into the wrong people?

899
01:11:43,111 --> 01:11:45,637
Who knows?
I mean, Mike always had secrets.

900
01:11:45,647 --> 01:11:49,908
You know, over there,
he was always sneaking off by himself.

901
01:11:49,918 --> 01:11:53,913
