for a whole two hours?

904
01:12:01,597 --> 01:12:05,499
Driving around,
looking for a party, or women.

905
01:12:05,667 --> 01:12:07,794
Did you stop anywhere?

906
01:12:09,471 --> 01:12:10,796
Yes, ma'am.

907
01:12:10,806 --> 01:12:12,806
[GULPS]

908
01:12:13,442 --> 01:12:15,603
