weapons and authority.

929
01:13:13,869 --> 01:13:17,362
You put men facedown in the dirt,
step on their backs, kick in doors.

930
01:13:17,372 --> 01:13:19,331
Somebody comes at you, you kill them.

931
01:13:19,341 --> 01:13:22,634
