charging at me, I'd reach for my weapon.

936
01:13:34,823 --> 01:13:37,349
KIRKLANDER: The interview is over.
-I'm glad none of this bothered you.

937
01:13:37,359 --> 01:13:40,285
I gotta tell you,
I saw my father come back from war.

938
01:13:40,295 --> 01:13:42,988
Things he couldn't deal with
pretty much destroyed him.

939
01:13:42,998 --> 01:13:45,223
-Huh. What was he, in Panama?
KIRKLANDER: Enough.

940
01:13:45,233 --> 01:13:47,459
You have no idea what we did,
and we did it for you.

941
01:13:47,469 --> 01:13:48,894
-For me?
